1
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:13,000
I want to see Tuoya.

2
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:16,410
Since you were able to find this place, Miss Shen,

3
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:19,140
you must be quite capable.

4
00:01:19,520 --> 00:01:22,800
But do you know the rules here?

5
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:24,920
Rules?

6
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:29,240
What rules?

7
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:34,440
If you want to see someone,

8
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:36,280
you have to beat me in a gamble first.

9
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:36,840
How?

10
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,560
Among these five cups,

11
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:43,560
one is lethal.

12
00:01:46,479 --> 00:01:47,560
Miss Shen,

13
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:50,220
you and I will take turns choosing a cup to drink.

14
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:52,440
If at any point you get scared

15
00:01:53,320 --> 00:01:54,360
and dare not drink,

16
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:55,360
you lose.

17
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,479
You are the guest.

18
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,800
Do you want to go first or second?

19
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:00,840
First.

20
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:35,200
Miss Shen, it seems you've lost.

21
00:02:36,360 --> 00:02:37,200
Wait a moment.

22
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:46,320
Your thoughts are too obvious, Boss Ji.

23
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:52,560
It seems you're not sure

24
00:02:53,040 --> 00:02:55,400
which one is the actual lethal cup.

25
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:57,450
Aren't you afraid of death?

26
00:02:57,800 --> 00:03:00,000
I just believe you value your life more.

27
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:02,970
You wouldn't actually use poison.

28
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:07,240
Interesting. Very interesting.

29
00:03:10,040 --> 00:03:14,080
Why go to such lengths just to see me?

30
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:17,360
I hate the feeling of my fate being in someone else's hands.

31
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:20,280
But how many people in this world

32
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:22,540
truly hold their fate in their own hands?

33
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:25,760
Your Yueshi Kingdom retreats in order to advance.

34
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:27,640
The marriage alliance is a sham.

35
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:30,560
Spying and seizing power is the truth.

36
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:34,120
Correct. Since you know everything,

37
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,600
why come to me?

38
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:38,760
Shouldn't you report this to your Emperor first?

39
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:41,520
Whatever happens to Dasheng

40
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,380
is none of my business.

41
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:47,040
You want status and power,

42
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:50,040
while I only want a person.

43
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:51,920
I wonder who you want, Miss Shen.

44
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,960
That's none of your concern.

45
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,680
If I cooperate with you,

46
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,720
what's in it for me?

47
00:03:58,040 --> 00:04:00,080
There is only one Wolf King on the prairie.

48
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:03,400
Surely you don't just want to be a kept dog.

49
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:09,560
I told you, touch me and you die.

50
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:12,880
Miss Shen, spare me!

51
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:14,080
Spare my life!

52
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:15,840
Miss Shen, have mercy!

53
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:17,440
I failed to recognize your greatness.

54
00:04:17,440 --> 00:04:18,570
Beat us or punish us,

55
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,279
just spare our miserable lives!

56
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:22,240
Miss Shen! Spare us!

57
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,160
Have mercy, Miss Shen!

58
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:25,360
Miss Shen, Madam Hua ordered us to do this!

59
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,240
She saw your beauty on the street

60
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:28,000
and ordered us to kidnap you.

61
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:28,760
No, Miss Shen!

62
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:30,040
I just run a shop!

63
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,240
I don't know anything!

64
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,840
I really didn't do anything!

65
00:04:33,159 --> 00:04:35,240
You're good at shifting the blame.

66
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:39,120
Did you ever imagine this day when you kidnapped me?

67
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:42,520
Miss Shen, spare us!

68
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,680
So you do know fear.

69
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:48,760
Too bad I don't like giving second chances.

70
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:50,159
Miss Shen.

71
00:04:50,159 --> 00:04:50,890
Shut them up.

72
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:53,360
You are still useful.

73
00:04:53,680 --> 00:04:54,409
Come with me.

74
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,480
Yes, yes, yes.

75
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:57,280
Miss Shen!

76
00:04:57,280 --> 00:04:58,960
Miss Shen, spare me!

77
00:04:58,960 --> 00:04:59,760
Miss Shen.

78
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:05,040
Work for me from now on.

79
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:06,980
As for today...

80
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:09,080
Don't speak of what shouldn't be spoken.

81
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:09,880
Yes.

82
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,840
It seems I was right.

83
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:18,840
The Lingbo Flower is poisonous.

84
00:05:19,880 --> 00:05:24,880
In a few days, our dynasty will hold the annual Literary Gathering.

85
00:05:24,880 --> 00:05:26,840
At that time, the children of the nobility

86
00:05:26,840 --> 00:05:27,770
will all attend.

87
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:29,600
I'm not going.

88
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:31,140
Then I won't go either.

89
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:32,200
Why not?

90
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,920
Literary Gathering, Literary Gathering.

91
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:37,960
It's just a bunch of officials' sons showing off their literary skills.

92
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:39,120
It's utterly dull.

93
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:42,760
Exactly. Nothing but pretentious pleasantries.

94
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:43,920
Very boring.

95
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,380
Father, I won't go either.

96
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,159
But this year's gathering

97
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:50,480
will be hosted personally by the Third Prince.

98
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,159
Who?

99
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:52,159
The Third Prince.

100
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:54,760
Not only will the Prince host it,

101
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:57,159
but he will also set the topics himself,

102
00:05:57,159 --> 00:05:59,440
and provide commentary throughout.

103
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:02,500
If someone makes a good impression on him...

104
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:05,640
Father, since the Third Prince is coming,

105
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,760
then I must certainly go.

106
00:06:12,760 --> 00:06:15,920
Brother, please have pity on me.

107
00:06:16,520 --> 00:06:17,400
No.

108
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,360
My good brother,

109
00:06:19,760 --> 00:06:21,480
just pity me, please.

110
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:24,560
You can't let me make a fool of myself all alone.

111
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:26,920
Why do you want me to accompany you for embarrassing things?

112
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,250
Husband, you should go.

113
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:30,400
Why?

114
00:06:30,400 --> 00:06:33,120
Because you need to astonish everyone at the gathering

115
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,840
and shine brilliantly.

116
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:35,800
Who do you mean?

117
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,560
Me?

118
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:52,240
Huanghuacai.

119
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:06,600
Why don't we do something interesting today?

120
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:11,680
Huanghuacai, you, you, you...

121
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:13,320
You really have a heavy hand.

122
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:15,240
What did you want to do, Husband?

123
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:20,160
Can't I just read books?

124
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:26,280
These principles are hollow and dull.

125
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:28,250
What is the use of reading them?

126
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,720
It's a waste of time.

127
00:07:31,320 --> 00:07:33,280
Have you read the Spring and Autumn Annals?

128
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:35,560
I was forced to read a few chapters when I was young, that's all.

129
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:36,620
Then let me ask you.

130
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:38,290
Zheng Bo made a mistake.

131
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,040
Why didn't Jing Hou kill him?

132
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,320
If he killed Zheng Bo,

133
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:43,480
it would instead make the feudal lords fearful,

134
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:45,000
and damage his own prestige.

135
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,680
How many times have you read this book?

136
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:49,040
I just read it for a few days when I was young.

137
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:52,280
Bai Manchuan, what kind of person are you, really?

138
00:07:58,320 --> 00:08:01,440
The world thinks Young Master Bai is a useless fop.

139
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:02,900
They believe it to be true,

140
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,380
and I am happy to be at ease.

141
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,240
Why?

142
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:06,600
Huanghuacai,

143
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:11,840
do you know how many eyes are watching the Bai Residence?

144
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,580
If I reveal my talents,

145
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:16,040
it would be inviting destruction.

146
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:19,520
In the end, I fear I couldn't even protect the Marquis Manor.

147
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:22,000
If you keep enduring silently like this,

148
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:25,130
the Bai family will eventually be in a precarious state.

149
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:26,840
Now that you have me to protect you,

150
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:28,120
you might as well try

151
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:30,800
how a truly smart person should act.

152
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,210
You really dare to trust me.

153
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,960
Bai Manchuan, I trust you.

154
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,039
I hope you will help me.

155
00:08:38,280 --> 00:08:40,520
Prince, Princess, you have come from afar.

156
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:42,360
Great Sheng treats you with courtesy.

157
00:08:42,360 --> 00:08:45,690
May I ask if you can state the purpose of your visit directly?

158
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,400
The purpose?

159
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:51,960
Naturally, we came for peace at the border.

160
00:08:52,280 --> 00:08:54,960
But if your country refuses to make any concessions,

161
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:56,760
how can we talk about sincerity?

162
00:08:57,920 --> 00:08:59,920
What is this sincerity

163
00:09:00,800 --> 00:09:01,920
you speak of, Prince?

164
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:03,800
You cede the three border cities

165
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:07,730
as a betrothal gift for my sister, Tuoya, to become Empress.

166
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:09,520
Naturally, all will be well.

167
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:13,640
Those three cities are where the people of Great Sheng live and survive.

168
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:14,770
How can we cede them?

169
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:15,640
Besides,

170
00:09:16,520 --> 00:09:20,580
the position of Empress is not something that can be given just like that.

171
00:09:23,960 --> 00:09:25,820
Then there is nothing to discuss.

172
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:27,640
First Prince,

173
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,880
we came here to solve problems,

174
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:32,480
not to be threatened.

175
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:35,410
We are sincerely here for peace talks.

176
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:37,240
You speak of ending the war,

177
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:40,000
but have your cavalry at the border retreated?

178
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:41,960
Massacring villages, burning cities,

179
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:43,440
kidnapping people, and looting grain.

180
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:46,520
Is this the sincerity you speak of?

181
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:48,450
The situation is different today.

182
00:09:48,520 --> 00:09:50,120
If you insist on resisting,

183
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:52,520
you are seeking your own suffering.

184
00:09:53,040 --> 00:09:54,840
Those words are too arrogant.

185
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,600
If you don't agree,

186
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,440
you can come and try us.

187
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:01,020
Enough!

188
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:02,800
If you came to Great Sheng

189
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:04,480
just to show off your power,

190
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:07,600
then you might as well never go back.

191
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,200
Third Prince,

192
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:13,450
the Emperor of Great Sheng isn't dead yet.

193
00:10:13,680 --> 00:10:15,280
Can you make such a decision?

194
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:18,200
I am the Crown Prince, appointed by my Royal Father to oversee the state.

195
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:20,600
Naturally, I have the authority to decide.

196
00:10:21,520 --> 00:10:22,380
Your Highness.

197
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:23,800
Prince.

198
00:10:23,800 --> 00:10:26,400
The peace talks need to be discussed at length.

199
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:31,200
Please, Prince and Princess, stay in Great Sheng for a while longer.

200
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:40,980
Unbelievable.

201
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:45,050
Chancellor, do you think there's any need to continue talking?

202
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:48,880
Your Highness, resorting to arms is not a long-term solution.

203
00:10:49,040 --> 00:10:52,760
In my view, the Yueshi Kingdom is also sincere about peace talks.

204
00:10:53,400 --> 00:10:55,800
His Majesty and Your Highness are both benevolent rulers.

205
00:10:55,800 --> 00:10:57,880
Surely, you will prioritize the safety of the people.
